title: Single-Cell Analysis of Sensory Experience Regulated Gene Expression in Mouse Visual Cortex
abstract: Single-cell (inDrops) analysis of primary visual cortex in visually stimulated mice
overall_design: 6-8 week old C57BL6/J mice were dark-reared for 7 days and exposed to light for 1h or 4h. Control mice were kept in the dark. V1 was dissected and single cell RNASeq performed.
summary: Single-cell (inDrops) analysis of primary visual cortex in visually stimulated mice
